All documentation for the Snippets Plugin is available online at
http://dokuwiki.org/plugin:snippets
author: Michael Klier 2009 - 2010
author Dominik Eckelmann 2012 - 2014
author: Myron Turner  2015 - present

This version of the snippets plugin enables user to choose have files with embedded snippets automatically updated when the snippet file is changed.  


